{"word":"H6424 - פָּלַס - pâlaç - paw-las' - Make","slug":"H6424","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">פָּלַס</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>pâlaç"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>paw-las'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Make"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E4;&#x05BC;&#x05DC;&#x05E1; - pa&#x0302;las</b> - <i>paw-las'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>roll</i> flat, that is, <i>prepare</i> (a road); also to <i>revolve</i>, that is, <i>weigh</i> (mentally): - make, ponder, weigh."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4657\">H4657</a>, <a href=\"#/H6425\">H6425</a>"}]}